item.title: Dumitru Vulpe | Resume
item.description: Bio Recent Computing graduate from University of Dundee and full stack developer with a strong points in Angular for the frontend and Nodejs, GoLang and Java for the backend; but also a lot of experience in other technologies and an eagerness to learn more. Main tech related interests are mostly in backend development, dev-ops, general programming/scripting, security and generally keeping up with tech news, specifically in the security, Open-Source and hardware sectors.
